994
00:56:45,200 --> 00:56:47,200
like the traditional dobos torte.

995
00:56:47,200 --> 00:56:48,600
It's worth a go.

996
00:56:54,880 --> 00:56:58,840
Let's see if I can get this knife through those 12 layers AND caramel.

